#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=How about as people ?
#Text=Yeah .
#Text=How so ?

#Text=Well , it affected me in the sense that I feel like it has changed where I have come from very much ; Denmark participated in it and sent soldiers to support the U.S. And I think that definitely made me aware of what a decision like that does to a country .
#Text=Now I think the Danish people are really confronted with having to redefine this strong sense of a Socialist heart that does n't seem as strong as it was .
#Text=Mmmm , well , not really .
#Text=I mean , I knew what America was in it for , and I disagreed with it .
#Text=It 's about money and oil and stuff like that .
#Text=And , they are just using the terrorist thing when it started as just a front , you know ?
#Text=I get much more affected not so much by war itself but when I hear about civilians involved in war .
#Text=But I was much more affected by stuff that happens in Chechnya , for instance .
#Text=I used to read a lot about that , and that is a forgotten war that really people do n't give a shit about .
#Text=Why do you have such a particular interest in Chechnya ?

#Text=Not particularly , I guess it was just after the school shooting and people were getting down on the Chechen rebels , and I 'm like , " Yeah , that was such a horrible thing to happen , all those innocent children , that was probably the worst ... "
#Text=Beslan was it ?
#Text=Yeah .
#Text=The thing is there was a reason for it , know what I mean ?
#Text=I 'm not justifying it any way because I know it is absolutely atrocious ...
#Text=But it was ideology and not oil ...
#Text=Yeah !
#Text=The reason for it was to show the world that there is a huge problem going on where we live and people do n't pay attention to it .
#Text=We are going to have to do something for you to take notice .
#Text=And what they did was just a very wrong way of doing it , but at least they grabbed a little attention for themselves .
#Text=But the only attention they got out of it was basically that Chechen rebels were murderers and child killers .
#Text=But the Russian soldiers rape and kill innocent Chechens every single day , and no one gives a damn about it .
#Text=Every single day !
#Text=Why do you think it 's not talked about ?
#Text=I actually do n't know , to be honest with you .
#Text=And I actually do n't know the world that well , and I 'm sure there are a lot of forgotten wars still raging in the world , so I do n't know , to be honest with you .
